{"id":"p025","sentences":[{"id":"09-nageki-no-bourei-1-p025-s0","tokens":[{"s":"担当","r":"たんとう","v":"v0247"},{"s":"編集","r":"へんしゅう","v":"v3002"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"川口","r":"かわぐち","v":"v3003"},{"s":"様","r":"さま","v":"v1140"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"My editor, Kawaguchi-sama."}},{"id":"09-nageki-no-bourei-1-p025-s1","tokens":[{"s":"そして","v":"v0149"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"出版","r":"しゅっぱん","v":"v3004"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"際し","r":"さいし","v":"v3005","lemma":"際する"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"尽力","r":"じんりょく","v":"v3006"},{"s":"いただきました","v":"v3007","lemma":"いただく"},{"s":"ＧＣノベルズ","v":"v3008"},{"s":"編集部","r":"へんしゅうぶ","v":"v3009"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"皆様","r":"みなさま","v":"v3010"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"関係","r":"かんけい","v":"v1439"},{"s":"各社","r":"かくしゃ","v":"v3011"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"皆様方","r":"みなさまがた","v":"v3012"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"And the staff of GC Novels' editorial department, and everyone at the related companies who lent their efforts to publication."}},{"id":"09-nageki-no-bourei-1-p025-s2","tokens":[{"s":"私","r":"わたし","v":"v0743"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"小説","r":"しょうせつ","v":"v3013"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"書く","r":"かく","v":"v0206"},{"s":"こと","v":"v0850"},{"s":"しか"},{"s":"出来ない","r":"できない","v":"v2633","lemma":"出来る"},{"s":"人間","r":"にんげん","v":"v0270"},{"s":"です"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"何","r":"なに","v":"v0167"},{"s":"から"},{"s":"何","r":"なに","v":"v0167"},{"s":"まで"},{"s":"お世話になりました","r":"おせわになりました","v":"v3014","lemma":"お世話になる"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"I'm a person who can only write — I've leaned on you for everything, top to bottom."}},{"id":"09-nageki-no-bourei-1-p025-s3","tokens":[{"s":"こうして","v":"v0369"},{"s":"拙作","r":"せっさく","v":"v2931"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"立派","r":"りっぱ","v":"v2627"},{"s":"な"},{"s":"一冊","r":"いっさつ","v":"v3015"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"本","r":"ほん","v":"v0059"},{"s":"として","v":"v2351"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"世","r":"よ","v":"v3016"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"出る","r":"でる","v":"v0709"},{"s":"こと","v":"v0850"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"なった","v":"v0008","lemma":"なる"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"皆様","r":"みなさま","v":"v3010"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"おかげ","v":"v0323"},{"s":"です"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"That my humble work has come into the world as such a fine bound book is thanks to you all."}},{"id":"09-nageki-no-bourei-1-p025-s4","tokens":[{"s":"本当に","r":"ほんとうに","v":"v2934"},{"s":"ありがとうございました","v":"v2996"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Truly, thank you very much."}},{"id":"09-nageki-no-bourei-1-p025-s5","tokens":[{"s":"今後","r":"こんご","v":"v3017"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"よろしくお願い致します","r":"よろしくおねがいいたします","v":"v3018"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"I look forward to continuing to work with you."}},{"id":"09-nageki-no-bourei-1-p025-s6","tokens":[{"s":"締切","r":"しめきり","v":"v3019"},{"s":"破らない","r":"やぶらない","v":"v2338","lemma":"破る"},{"s":"ように","v":"v2969"},{"s":"気をつけます","r":"きをつけます","v":"v2915","lemma":"気をつける"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"I'll be careful not to break deadlines.","note":"A small joke at the end of the formal acknowledgement, breaking register — typical light-novel afterword warmth."}}]}
